---
title: Double Louisiana Chicken & Cheesy Lemon Crushed Potatoes with Corn Slaw & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: A mashed potato is a classic but wouldn’t it be fun if we tried something a little different tonight? Why not crush the potatoes
instead with a squeeze of lemon for a extra zap, they’ll go nicely with the seasoned chicken and balanced by a sweetcorn
salad. This will become the only way you’ll want your potatoes and chicken.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64c3569528bfd46507f0ab08-a9f24ec0.jpeg
